divs: sighting detailsi happened to be in my bathroom and looked out at the sky as i always do and there was that strange circle of bright light. i watched it for a few minutes and then it went sideways to the other bright light. this was south\southeast. then on nov.10 2008 the exact same thing happened, the same positions. we have our airport pretty much in that area. it used to be a military field. the manchester airport now. i called the police station, they said it was not their job i knew it was a ufo. i got tired of watching it and went back to bed. i am not afraid of ufo's. regards, ann e estee
